metadata.name: The Jasper’s
metadata.description:
The Jasper’s 

Meet the Jasper family, a group of card-loving degenerates who can't get enough of their favorite pastime.

 From grandpa's endless poker games to mom's weekly NFT flip tournaments, there's never a dull moment in this household. 

But don't let their love of cards fool you - they're also a family of mischievous pranksters who love to pull practical jokes on each other. 

Whether they're hustling each other at the card table or sneaking up on grandma with a whoopee cushion, there's never a dull moment. 

So if you're looking for a wild and wacky family to join in on a game of cards, look no further than the Jasper clan.

They are a Beautiful Disaster.
